title: Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview
summary:
Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview

The Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview (I/O edition) has been released by Google Developers, featuring enhanced coding capabilities for developers to start building with before Google I/O later this month. The update includes improvements in front-end and UI development, as well as transforming and editing code, and creating sophisticated agentic workflows. Gemini 2.5 Pro now ranks #1 on the WebDev Arena leaderboard and powers Cursor's innovative code agent. The model delivers state-of-the-art video understanding, scoring 84.8% on the VideoMME benchmark, and is strong at front-end web development, helping developers get more done. The new version of Gemini 2.5 Pro addresses key developer feedback and includes improved coding performance. Developers can build with Gemini 2.5 Pro using the Gemini API in Google AI Studio, and enterprise customers can use Vertex AI.
